            | "France Festival Distribution" is strictly forbiden to |
            | distribute or redistribute AppISizer or any other      |
            | file or program created by me, Gérard Cornu.           |
            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

@endnode
