  FRED FISH and the AmigaLibDisk Library:
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

   As Fred has been releasing CDROMs from a while now, just choose
   carefully your Fish CDs retailers, if you don't buy them directly
